Package: lazyvec
Type: Package
Title: A simple R interface to the ALTREP framework
Version: 0.1.5
Date: 2019-06-15
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mark", "Klik", email = "markklik@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")))
Description: Provides a toolset for creating custom ALTREP vectors without any knowledge of R's
    internal (ALTREP) C API. Includes a monitoring framework for internal ALTREP calls.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
License: AGPL-3 | file LICENSE
Imports:
    Rcpp (>=  0.12.18.3),
    crayon
Suggests:
    testthat,
    lintr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
URL: https://fstpackage.github.io/lazyvec
BugReports: https://github.com/fstpackage/lazyvec/issues
